Package: phonfeatures
Title: Assign articulatory features to phonetic characters
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Rasmus", "Puggaard-Rode", , "r.puggaard@phonetik.uni-muenchen.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4522-9987"))
Description: Adds columns with articulatory features to a data frame based on phonetic transcription.
    Default articulatory features are already defined, but the user can also add 
    non-standard X-SAMPA characters or change the default feature values.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/rpuggaardrode/phonfeatures
BugReports: https://github.com/rpuggaardrode/phonfeatures/issues
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ipa,
    stringr
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
LazyData: true
